    • Field Detail

      • GSON

        public static final com.google.gson.Gson GSON

        Gson instance. Do you even need an explanation?

        Includes the following goodies:
        • Exclusion strategy for excluding fields annotated with the Exclude annotation.
        • Type adapter for Identifiers, to serialize and deserialize them via their string representation.
        • Complex map key serialization.
        • Support for serializing special floating point values.
        • Support for non-standard JSON features when deserializing.
        • snake_case field naming policy.
        • Pretty printing!

      • GSON_COMPRESSED

        public static final com.google.gson.Gson GSON_COMPRESSED

        Gson instance for "compressed" JSON.

        Has the same features as GSON, but without pretty printing.

        3.0.0
